Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.16,0:01:04.08,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(419.493,462.667)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:01:07.79,0:01:09.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.79,0:01:09.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait for it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.76,0:01:23.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fad(988,0)\pos(612,866)}准时百分比
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.56,0:01:23.47,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\pos(920,864)}100%
Dialogue: 1,0:01:26.56,0:01:28.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,新的一天也会偏头痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.56,0:01:28.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Another day, another migraine
Dialogue: 1,0:01:30.36,0:01:30.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,偏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.36,0:01:30.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mi
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.40,0:01:34.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fad(988,0)\pos(612,866)}准时百分比
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.15,0:01:34.36,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\fnArial\pos(920,864)}12%
Dialogue: 1,0:01:34.78,0:01:35.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,头痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.78,0:01:35.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,graine
Dialogue: 1,0:01:37.74,0:01:41.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在蟹堡王上班是不是很棒啊  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.74,0:01:41.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't it great working at the Krusty Krab, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:42.33,0:01:43.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.33,0:01:43.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't it?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:43.58,0:01:44.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,在这上班
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.58,0:01:44.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Working here?
Dialogue: 1,0:01:44.83,0:01:45.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.83,0:01:45.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, great
Dialogue: 1,0:01:45.66,0:01:47.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.66,0:01:47.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.00,0:01:47.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.00,0:01:47.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:01:47.71,0:01:48.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.71,0:01:48.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:01:48.54,0:01:49.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你先等着  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.54,0:01:49.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold that thought, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:01:49.79,0:01:52.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我一大早还得去停船场志愿捡垃圾呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.79,0:01:50.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm due in the parking lot
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.88,0:01:52.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for early morning litter patrol
Dialogue: 1,0:01:52.60,0:01:54.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,愿海神王闪耀在我的收获之上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.60,0:01:54.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,May Neptune shine brightly on my harvest
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.30,0:02:00.09,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(920,172)}垃圾烦死我
Dialogue: 1,0:01:58.76,0:01:59.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,垃圾
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.76,0:01:59.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Litter
Dialogue: 1,0:02:00.51,0:02:02.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看来有谁很想念垃圾篓子了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.51,0:02:02.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks like someone missed the trash basket
Dialogue: 1,0:02:02.31,0:02:03.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对吧  糖果包装纸先生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.31,0:02:03.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,huh, Mr. Candy Wrapper?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:04.35,0:02:05.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在的小孩子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.35,0:02:05.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kids these days
Dialogue: 1,0:02:07.35,0:02:09.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这么猖獗的我还没见过
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.35,0:02:09.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've never seen such an epidemic
Dialogue: 1,0:02:09.40,0:02:11.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,起码也不会再继续扔了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.40,0:02:11.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, at least it's all over now
Dialogue: 1,0:02:24.49,0:02:27.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这些垃圾都是哪来的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.49,0:02:27.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where is all this litter coming from?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:32.04,0:02:34.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有我在  你休想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:34.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not on my watch
Dialogue: 1,0:02:34.43,0:02:35.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先生我跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.43,0:02:35.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sir, I will have you know
Dialogue: 1,0:02:35.84,0:02:37.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,乱扔垃圾是违法的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.84,0:02:37.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,it's against the law to litter
Dialogue: 1,0:02:38.22,0:02:40.01,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你又能拿我怎么办  报警吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.22,0:02:40.01,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do, call the police?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:41.80,0:02:42.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.80,0:02:42.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes
Dialogue: 1,0:02:48.89,0:02:51.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎样了  小警察
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:51.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's it going, lieutenant?
Dialogue: 1,0:02:51.03,0:02:53.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这么说吧  我希望那个乱扔垃圾的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.03,0:02:53.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, let's just say I hope our litterbug there
Dialogue: 1,0:02:53.61,0:02:56.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,留了点肚子去吃甜点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.61,0:02:56.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,saved room for his just desserts
Dialogue: 1,0:02:57.40,0:02:58.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.40,0:02:58.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:02:58.28,0:03:00.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,甜点
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:03:00.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just desserts
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.28,0:03:00.07,注释,,0,0,0,,[ desserts（甜点）\N与 just deserts（罪有应得）谐音 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:03:01.07,0:03:01.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,随你便
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.07,0:03:01.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatever
Dialogue: 1,0:03:02.53,0:03:04.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  你难道不知道他是谁吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.53,0:03:04.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, don't you know who that is?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:04.87,0:03:05.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:05.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:05.76,0:03:08.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他就是告密掐脖复仇者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.76,0:03:08.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the Tattletale Strangler
Dialogue: 1,0:03:08.34,0:03:08.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.34,0:03:08.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:09.13,0:03:10.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,告密掐脖复仇者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.13,0:03:10.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Tattletale Strangler
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.67,0:03:12.46,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(688,314)}通缉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.67,0:03:12.46,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1162,902)}告密掐脖复仇者
Dialogue: 1,0:03:11.09,0:03:14.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他发过誓要掐死送他坐牢的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.09,0:03:14.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's promised to strangle anyone who turns him in
Dialogue: 1,0:03:17.21,0:03:19.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他貌似有点气咱们  章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.21,0:03:19.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He seems kind of angry with us, eh, Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:20.51,0:03:21.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.51,0:03:21.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:22.18,0:03:22.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.18,0:03:22.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.22,0:03:24.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,坐苦牢去吧  复仇者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.22,0:03:24.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're going to do time, Strangler
Dialogue: 1,0:03:24.76,0:03:26.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,苦死你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.76,0:03:26.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hard time
Dialogue: 1,0:03:26.81,0:03:28.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,警官们好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.81,0:03:28.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hi, officers
Dialogue: 1,0:03:28.35,0:03:29.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以他是不是要去坐牢了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.35,0:03:29.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So he's going to jail, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:29.95,0:03:31.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁  复仇者吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.95,0:03:31.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who, Strangler?
Dialogue: 1,0:03:31.41,0:03:32.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  复仇者
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.41,0:03:32.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Strangler
Dialogue: 1,0:03:32.54,0:03:33.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:33.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:03:33.44,0:03:35.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他得去坐好长时间的牢呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.44,0:03:35.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's going to jail for a long time
Dialogue: 1,0:03:36.52,0:03:37.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,跟我一模一样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.52,0:03:37.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That looks like me
Dialogue: 1,0:03:44.95,0:03:46.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放心好了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.95,0:03:46.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:03:46.28,0:03:48.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他可掐不到你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.28,0:03:48.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he won't be able to strangle you
Dialogue: 1,0:03:48.20,0:03:50.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  他被铐得可严实了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.20,0:03:50.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, we got him chained up real good
Dialogue: 1,0:03:50.54,0:03:51.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,绝对逃不走的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.54,0:03:51.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He'll never get away
Dialogue: 1,0:03:52.58,0:03:53.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.58,0:03:53.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Not again
Dialogue: 1,0:03:53.46,0:03:54.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  他逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:54.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yup, he got away
Dialogue: 1,0:03:58.63,0:04:01.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两位好心警官会保护我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:04:01.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You nice officers will protect me, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:01.22,0:04:02.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们可不是保镖  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.22,0:04:02.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We ain't bodyguards, kid
Dialogue: 1,0:04:03.34,0:04:05.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对  再看到他就打电话找我们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.34,0:04:05.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, give us a call if you see him again
Dialogue: 1,0:04:05.86,0:04:07.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,告密人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.86,0:04:07.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,tattletale
Dialogue: 1,0:04:10.60,0:04:12.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那些警官说得对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:12.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Those officers are right
Dialogue: 1,0:04:12.20,0:04:13.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我需要保镖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.20,0:04:13.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need a bodyguard
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:15.73,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(524,374)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:04:13.62,0:04:15.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.62,0:04:15.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:04:15.99,0:04:17.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有疯子盯上我了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.99,0:04:17.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's a maniac after me
Dialogue: 1,0:04:17.80,0:04:19.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我需要保镖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.80,0:04:19.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need a bodyguard
Dialogue: 1,0:04:21.53,0:04:25.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在海军得五次金钳奖不是没道理的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:25.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I wasn't five-time golden claws in the navy for nothing
Dialogue: 1,0:04:25.87,0:04:27.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等他看到我动手
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.87,0:04:27.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,When he see me moves
Dialogue: 1,0:04:27.33,0:04:29.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定会落荒而逃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.33,0:04:29.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,he'll be running scared
Dialogue: 1,0:04:29.54,0:04:31.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以你说的小恶棍在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:31.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So where is this little bully
Dialogue: 1,0:04:31.54,0:04:32.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,公园里吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:32.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,down at the park?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:32.79,0:04:33.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,汽水店吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.79,0:04:33.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The soda shop?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:34.12,0:04:36.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他长什么样  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:36.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What does he look like, eh, boy?
Dialogue: 1,0:04:36.46,0:04:37.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这就是他  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.46,0:04:37.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This would be him, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:39.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(740,384)}通缉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.88,0:04:39.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1020,956)}告密掐脖复仇者
Dialogue: 1,0:04:39.00,0:04:41.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,告密掐脖复仇者
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:41.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Tattletale Strangler
Dialogue: 1,0:04:41.11,0:04:42.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝你走开
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:42.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Go away, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:04:42.88,0:04:45.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带走你的死亡阴云
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.88,0:04:45.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take your death cloud with you
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:58.94,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(744,172)}狂暴酒馆
Dialogue: 1,0:04:56.02,0:04:57.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求抱抱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.02,0:04:57.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hold me
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.02,0:05:04.90,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(368,396)}公交站
Dialogue: 1,0:05:00.02,0:05:02.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就这样了  我得离开裤头村
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.02,0:05:02.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's it, I got to get out of town
Dialogue: 1,0:05:02.24,0:05:04.05,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等找到保镖再回来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.24,0:05:04.05,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,till I can find a bodyguard
Dialogue: 1,0:05:04.05,0:05:04.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保镖是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.05,0:05:04.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bodyguard, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:05.40,0:05:07.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我应该可以帮上你的忙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.40,0:05:07.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I might be able to help you out
Dialogue: 1,0:05:07.09,0:05:08.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你不明白  先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.09,0:05:08.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't understand, mister
Dialogue: 1,0:05:08.49,0:05:11.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,镇上最可怕的人要伤我  我需要保护
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.49,0:05:11.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I need protection from the scariest guy in town
Dialogue: 1,0:05:11.41,0:05:12.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是他照片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.41,0:05:12.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's his picture
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.79,0:05:15.75,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(418,266)}通缉
Dialogue: 1,0:05:14.21,0:05:15.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他不是很能打的样子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.21,0:05:15.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He doesn't look so tough
Dialogue: 1,0:05:16.01,0:05:17.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我举报了他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.01,0:05:17.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I tattled on him
Dialogue: 1,0:05:17.12,0:05:21.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在他想心狠手辣掐死我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:18.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and now he wants to strangle me
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:21.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,with his diabolical hands
Dialogue: 1,0:05:21.13,0:05:23.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,希望他手不脏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:23.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I hope they're not dirty
Dialogue: 1,0:05:30.97,0:05:33.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这边目击者太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:33.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's too many witnesses around here
Dialogue: 1,0:05:33.35,0:05:34.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小子我跟你说
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.35,0:05:34.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Listen, kid
Dialogue: 1,0:05:34.27,0:05:35.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可以当你保镖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.27,0:05:35.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I could be your bodyguard
Dialogue: 1,0:05:36.14,0:05:37.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我名片
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.14,0:05:37.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here's my card
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:39.94,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(850,720)}保镖
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:39.94,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(916,328)}告密掐脖复仇者
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.23,0:05:39.94,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\p1\bord0\c&H000000&\blur1\pos(1089.142,318.286)\frz80.66}m 0 0 l 7 0 7 350 0 350{\p0}
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.23,0:05:39.94,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\p1\bord0\c&H000000&\blur1\frz103.8\pos(1083.142,250.286)}m 0 0 l 7 0 7 350 0 350{\p0}
Dialogue: 1,0:05:38.23,0:05:39.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我觉得不错
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.23,0:05:39.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Looks good to me
Dialogue: 1,0:05:40.11,0:05:41.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,录用你了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.11,0:05:41.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're hired
Dialogue: 1,0:05:41.37,0:05:42.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我已经觉得安全多了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.37,0:05:42.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I feel safer already
Dialogue: 1,0:05:42.65,0:05:43.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,接着要干啥
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:43.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What's next?
Dialogue: 1,0:05:43.57,0:05:45.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那疯子可能无处不在
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.57,0:05:45.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, the maniac could be anywhere
Dialogue: 1,0:05:45.76,0:05:47.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,穿着伪装
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.76,0:05:47.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,wearing a disguise
Dialogue: 1,0:05:47.25,0:05:48.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他可能是那个老头
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.25,0:05:48.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He could be that old man
Dialogue: 1,0:05:48.91,0:05:49.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者那个婴儿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.91,0:05:49.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or that baby
Dialogue: 1,0:05:49.95,0:05:51.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者那颗石块
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.95,0:05:51.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or that pebble
Dialogue: 1,0:05:51.17,0:05:52.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者那根树枝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.17,0:05:52.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or that stick
Dialogue: 1,0:05:52.16,0:05:55.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,或者那张坑蒙拐骗胡子店的小票
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.16,0:05:53.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Or that receipt
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.24,0:05:55.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for the Phony Baloney Mustache Emporium
Dialogue: 1,0:05:56.04,0:05:56.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是我的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:56.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's mine
Dialogue: 1,0:05:57.00,0:06:00.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保镖啊  我现在受到你严密的保护了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.00,0:06:00.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, bodyguard, my body is in your guarding hands
Dialogue: 1,0:06:00.23,0:06:01.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要先干啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.23,0:06:01.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do we do first?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:01.71,0:06:04.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,建议去一个比较僻静的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.71,0:06:04.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I suggest we go to a nice quiet, secluded location
Dialogue: 1,0:06:05.30,0:06:08.19,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,比如垃圾箱后边  或者黑暗的小巷子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:08.19,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,like behind an old dumpster, or a dark alley
Dialogue: 1,0:06:08.19,0:06:10.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以来我家把灯全都关了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.19,0:06:10.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We could go to my house and turn off all the lights
Dialogue: 1,0:06:10.73,0:06:11.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:11.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:06:11.83,0:06:14.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样就不会有谁听到你被掐死
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.83,0:06:14.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That way no one could hear you being strangled
Dialogue: 1,0:06:14.60,0:06:15.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.60,0:06:15.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:06:15.39,0:06:15.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,受保护
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.39,0:06:15.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,protected
Dialogue: 1,0:06:17.77,0:06:18.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,完美
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.77,0:06:18.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Perfect
Dialogue: 1,0:06:20.94,0:06:22.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错  好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.94,0:06:22.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yes, excellent
Dialogue: 1,0:06:33.66,0:06:35.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我得先要办点事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.66,0:06:35.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But first I got to do a few errands
Dialogue: 1,0:06:36.04,0:06:37.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那行  不过要快点
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.04,0:06:37.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, but let's make it quick
Dialogue: 1,0:06:37.62,0:06:39.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的天性就是快
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.62,0:06:39.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Quick" is my middle name
Dialogue: 1,0:06:39.79,0:06:42.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来看看  纸巾
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.79,0:06:42.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's see, paper towels
Dialogue: 1,0:06:42.76,0:06:45.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这包写的是  附近最好的卫生纸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.76,0:06:45.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This one says, "Best paper towel around"
Dialogue: 1,0:06:45.55,0:06:48.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这包写的是  全镇最好的卫生纸
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.55,0:06:48.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This one says, "Best paper towel in town"
Dialogue: 1,0:06:48.72,0:06:49.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全镇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:49.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"In town"
Dialogue: 1,0:06:50.09,0:06:50.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,附近
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.09,0:06:50.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Around"
Dialogue: 1,0:06:51.39,0:06:52.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全镇
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:52.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"In town"
Dialogue: 1,0:06:52.85,0:06:53.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,附近
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.85,0:06:53.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Around"
Dialogue: 1,0:06:53.77,0:06:55.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你怎么看  保镖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.77,0:06:55.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What do you think, bodyguard?
Dialogue: 1,0:06:55.85,0:06:58.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能快点进你家门就行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.85,0:06:58.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Whatever gets us to your house quicker
Dialogue: 1,0:06:58.70,0:07:00.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那我全买了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.70,0:07:00.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'll take both
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.31,0:07:02.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(260,716)}干洗  请稍候
Dialogue: 1,0:07:00.81,0:07:02.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给你  海绵宝宝先生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.81,0:07:02.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here you go, Mr. SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:07:04.15,0:07:05.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哪里有问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:05.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is there something wrong?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:05.36,0:07:08.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不太确定这是不是我的裤子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:08.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if these are my pants
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.82,0:07:13.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(366,324)}香水
Dialogue: 1,0:07:13.70,0:07:15.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这份怎么样  保镖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.70,0:07:15.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How about this one, bodyguard?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.08,0:07:15.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太难闻了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.08,0:07:15.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too overbearing?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:15.99,0:07:18.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就不能直接到你家去吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.99,0:07:18.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Can we just go to your house?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:20.16,0:07:22.33,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到了  海绵府
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.16,0:07:22.33,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here we are, SquarePants Manor
Dialogue: 1,0:07:22.33,0:07:25.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保镖  让我借着这个机会
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.33,0:07:25.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bodyguard, let me just take this opportunity
Dialogue: 1,0:07:25.07,0:07:28.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对你说  你这保镖强到人人都想要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.07,0:07:26.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,to say you're the best bodyguard
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.84,0:07:28.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,a fellow could hope to have
Dialogue: 1,0:07:28.63,0:07:31.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,少给我讲肉麻话
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:31.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, enough of the sappy talk
Dialogue: 1,0:07:31.09,0:07:33.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把门打开  这样我才能掐死你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.09,0:07:33.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Open the door so I can strangle you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:33.64,0:07:34.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.64,0:07:34.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.26,0:07:34.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,呛死你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.26,0:07:34.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,choke you
Dialogue: 1,0:07:34.76,0:07:35.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.76,0:07:35.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean, uh
Dialogue: 1,0:07:35.72,0:07:36.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,掐坏你气管
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:36.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,crush your windpipe
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.04,0:07:37.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.04,0:07:37.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean
Dialogue: 1,0:07:37.40,0:07:38.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保护我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.40,0:07:38.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Protect me?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:38.64,0:07:39.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:39.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks
Dialogue: 1,0:07:39.36,0:07:40.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别客气  复仇者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.36,0:07:40.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it, Strangler
Dialogue: 1,0:07:41.31,0:07:42.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是说保镖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.31,0:07:42.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I mean "bodyguard"
Dialogue: 1,0:07:42.56,0:07:44.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我把钥匙放哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.56,0:07:44.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, where did I put my key?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:45.40,0:07:47.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,二十分钟后
Dialogue: 1,0:07:49.15,0:07:50.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找不到啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.15,0:07:50.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, I can't find them
Dialogue: 1,0:07:51.24,0:07:52.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要来看下吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.24,0:07:52.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you want to take a look?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:52.78,0:07:53.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别管钥匙了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:53.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forget the key
Dialogue: 1,0:07:54.49,0:07:56.12,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爬窗户得了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:56.12,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's climb through this window
Dialogue: 1,0:07:57.16,0:07:58.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我够不着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:07:58.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't reach it
Dialogue: 1,0:07:58.74,0:08:00.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,能跳到我肩膀上面来吗  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:08:00.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Do you think you can you hop up on my shoulders, kid?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:00.80,0:08:01.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.80,0:08:01.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure
Dialogue: 1,0:08:01.66,0:08:04.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,穿上带刺的钉鞋  一切皆有可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:04.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,With these spiky cleats, anything is possible
Dialogue: 1,0:08:06.04,0:08:06.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,钉鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.04,0:08:06.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,"Cleats"?
Dialogue: 1,0:08:08.71,0:08:10.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,把脚从我眼窝里拿开
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:10.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get your feet out of my eye sockets
Dialogue: 1,0:08:10.94,0:08:14.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我尽力了  可我鞋卡你眼角膜里了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.94,0:08:14.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm trying, but my cleats are stuck in your corneas
Dialogue: 1,0:08:19.29,0:08:19.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:19.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get off
Dialogue: 1,0:08:20.32,0:08:21.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,下去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.32,0:08:21.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Get off
Dialogue: 1,0:08:21.48,0:08:23.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,六小时后
Dialogue: 1,0:08:31.07,0:08:32.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别生气了  保镖
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.07,0:08:32.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't be mad, bodyguard
Dialogue: 1,0:08:32.96,0:08:35.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我去拿放地毯底下的钥匙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.96,0:08:35.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let me just grab the key I keep under the mat
Dialogue: 1,0:08:35.16,0:08:36.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样就能进去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.16,0:08:36.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and we can get inside
Dialogue: 1,0:08:40.54,0:08:42.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,找到你了  你个小坏蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.54,0:08:42.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There you are, you little rascal
Dialogue: 1,0:08:42.38,0:08:43.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,现在把钥匙插进锁里
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.38,0:08:43.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now to put it in the lock
Dialogue: 1,0:08:43.87,0:08:45.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,激活制动栓
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:45.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,which should activate the tumblers
Dialogue: 1,0:08:45.08,0:08:46.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,然后就能开门了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.08,0:08:46.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,thus opening the door
Dialogue: 1,0:08:48.13,0:08:49.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,踏进去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.13,0:08:49.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Step inside
Dialogue: 1,0:08:50.34,0:08:52.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,关上门
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:52.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Close the door
Dialogue: 1,0:08:53.26,0:08:54.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好  我们到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.26,0:08:54.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, here we are
Dialogue: 1,0:08:54.93,0:08:58.18,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我总算让你孤身一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.93,0:08:58.18,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I finally got you all alone
Dialogue: 1,0:09:01.93,0:09:04.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  是不是很棒
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.93,0:09:04.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know, isn't it great?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:12.94,0:09:16.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这下可要遭报应了  告密人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.94,0:09:16.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now you're going to get yours, tattletale
Dialogue: 1,0:09:16.61,0:09:18.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,惊喜
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:18.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Surprise
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:20.53,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(814,170)}恭喜海绵宝宝{\fnArial}100%{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}准时
Dialogue: 1,0:09:21.20,0:09:26.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,庆祝我百分百准时上班的惊喜派对
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.20,0:09:23.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A surprise party to celebrate
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.87,0:09:26.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my perfect on-time percentage at work?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:26.87,0:09:28.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们怎么知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:28.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How'd you guys know?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:28.38,0:09:30.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是你送我们的邀请函上写的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.38,0:09:30.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's on the invitations you sent us
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.50,0:09:30.88,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(620,702)}派对
Dialogue: 1,0:09:30.96,0:09:32.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来跳舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.96,0:09:32.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's boogie
Dialogue: 1,0:09:41.72,0:09:43.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家再见  谢谢参加
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:43.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye, everybody, thanks for coming
Dialogue: 1,0:09:43.77,0:09:44.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.77,0:09:44.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bye, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:09:44.93,0:09:45.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见痞老板
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.93,0:09:45.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,bye, Plankton
Dialogue: 1,0:09:45.64,0:09:46.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见珊迪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.64,0:09:46.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,bye, Sandy
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.31,0:09:46.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见拉里
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.31,0:09:46.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,bye, Larry
Dialogue: 1,0:09:46.98,0:09:47.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见珍珍
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.98,0:09:47.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,bye, Pearl
Dialogue: 1,0:09:47.60,0:09:48.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见泡芙老师
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.60,0:09:48.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,bye, Mrs. Puff
Dialogue: 1,0:09:48.35,0:09:49.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见章鱼哥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.35,0:09:49.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,bye, Squidward
Dialogue: 1,0:09:49.06,0:09:50.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再见  剩下的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.06,0:09:50.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,bye, the rest
Dialogue: 1,0:09:54.78,0:09:56.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,总算孤身一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.78,0:09:56.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alone at last
Dialogue: 1,0:09:56.50,0:09:56.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.50,0:09:56.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:57.91,0:09:58.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.91,0:09:58.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:09:59.78,0:10:01.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,所以就剩咱俩了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:01.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So we're all alone now?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:01.76,0:10:03.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,只有你跟我还有地板了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.76,0:10:03.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Just you, me and the floorboards
Dialogue: 1,0:10:08.71,0:10:09.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.71,0:10:09.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:10:14.71,0:10:17.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生日快乐  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.71,0:10:17.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Happy birthday, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:10:17.56,0:10:19.84,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们怎么知道今天我生日的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.56,0:10:19.84,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How did you guys know today is my birthday?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:20.09,0:10:22.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们只是照着邀请函上写的做而已
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.09,0:10:22.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We just do what the invitations say
Dialogue: 1,0:10:22.69,0:10:24.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,再来跳舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.69,0:10:24.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's boogie some more
Dialogue: 1,0:10:35.61,0:10:37.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢谢到来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.61,0:10:37.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming
Dialogue: 1,0:10:39.32,0:10:40.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,又孤身一人了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.32,0:10:40.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Alone again
Dialogue: 1,0:10:40.71,0:10:41.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.71,0:10:41.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Is it true?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:42.12,0:10:43.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全都走了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.12,0:10:43.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Everybody's gone?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:44.16,0:10:45.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,今天没别的派对了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.16,0:10:45.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No more parties today?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:45.70,0:10:46.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要的东西全买到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.70,0:10:46.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You've got everything you need now?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.87,0:10:49.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一个人都不剩吗  彻底只剩咱俩吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.87,0:10:49.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nobody's left, we're completely alone?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:49.64,0:10:50.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.64,0:10:50.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:10:50.55,0:10:52.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这样的话
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.55,0:10:52.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,In that case
Dialogue: 1,0:10:55.05,0:10:56.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派对很好玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.05,0:10:56.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great parties, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:10:57.01,0:10:58.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对不起  小胖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.01,0:10:58.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sorry, tubby
Dialogue: 1,0:10:58.42,0:10:59.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:10:59.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you got to go
Dialogue: 1,0:10:59.26,0:11:00.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  可以相信派大星的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.26,0:11:00.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, we can trust Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:11:00.97,0:11:02.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他可是我最好的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:02.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's my best friend
Dialogue: 1,0:11:02.40,0:11:04.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我可不能冒这么大的险
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.40,0:11:04.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, uh, I can't take any chances
Dialogue: 1,0:11:04.32,0:11:06.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说不定  他就是复仇者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.32,0:11:06.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,For all we know, uh, he could be the Strangler
Dialogue: 1,0:11:06.89,0:11:08.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我是复仇者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:08.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the Strangler?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:09.06,0:11:10.02,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我早该知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.06,0:11:10.02,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I should have known
Dialogue: 1,0:11:10.35,0:11:11.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得去自首
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:11.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to turn myself in
Dialogue: 1,0:11:15.57,0:11:17.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来派大星是复仇者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.57,0:11:17.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So Patrick's the Strangler
Dialogue: 1,0:11:17.91,0:11:19.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,知人知面不知心
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.91,0:11:19.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee, you think you know a guy
Dialogue: 1,0:11:19.50,0:11:21.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他不是复仇者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.50,0:11:21.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's not the Strangler
Dialogue: 1,0:11:21.80,0:11:22.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.80,0:11:22.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He's not?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:23.41,0:11:25.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.41,0:11:25.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I am
Dialogue: 1,0:11:26.20,0:11:27.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你没剃须膏怎么做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.20,0:11:27.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How'd you do that without shaving cream?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:28.13,0:11:29.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是假胡子  你个白痴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.13,0:11:29.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's a fake, you idiot
Dialogue: 1,0:11:29.79,0:11:31.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我到派对商店买的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.79,0:11:31.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I bought it at the party store
Dialogue: 1,0:11:32.04,0:11:33.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有谁说了派对吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:33.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Did someone say "party"?
Dialogue: 1,0:11:36.96,0:11:37.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我受不了了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:37.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I can't take it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:38.96,0:11:41.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保镖别走  我需要保护
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:41.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, bodyguard, I need protection
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.51,0:11:45.18,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(890,394)}出租船
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.05,0:11:42.97,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快开船
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.05,0:11:42.97,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Step on it
Dialogue: 1,0:11:42.97,0:11:44.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有个疯子在追我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:44.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm being chased by a maniac
Dialogue: 1,0:11:45.30,0:11:46.68,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不安全
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:46.68,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not safe
Dialogue: 1,0:11:46.68,0:11:48.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回来
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.68,0:11:48.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come back
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.35,0:11:50.98,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(606,326)}裤头村机场
Dialogue: 1,0:11:52.10,0:11:53.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终于啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.10,0:11:53.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Finally
Dialogue: 1,0:11:53.65,0:11:55.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,远离那家伙了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.65,0:11:55.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Away from that guy
Dialogue: 1,0:11:55.29,0:11:56.38,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好办法啊  保镖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.29,0:11:56.38,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good idea, bodyguard
Dialogue: 1,0:11:56.38,0:11:57.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他肯定发现不到咱在上面
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.38,0:11:57.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He'll never find us up here
Dialogue: 1,0:12:04.45,0:12:05.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想得真周到  保镖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:05.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good thinking, bodyguard
Dialogue: 1,0:12:05.59,0:12:07.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,复仇者可能就在那座飞机上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.59,0:12:07.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Strangler could have been on that plane
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.20,0:12:10.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(732,438)}警察局
Dialogue: 1,0:12:11.25,0:12:12.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,保镖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.25,0:12:12.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bodyguard
Dialogue: 1,0:12:12.54,0:12:13.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,听好  小子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.54,0:12:13.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Look, kid
Dialogue: 1,0:12:14.67,0:12:17.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不是你保镖
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.67,0:12:17.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm not your bodyguard
Dialogue: 1,0:12:19.51,0:12:21.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就是复仇者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.51,0:12:21.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm the Strangler
Dialogue: 1,0:12:21.81,0:12:22.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看见没
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.81,0:12:22.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,See?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:24.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(784,138)}通缉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:24.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(772,980)}告密掐脖复仇者
Dialogue: 1,0:12:24.84,0:12:26.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,复仇者
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.84,0:12:26.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Strangler
Dialogue: 1,0:12:26.98,0:12:28.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,干得漂亮  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.98,0:12:28.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good work, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:12:28.51,0:12:30.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你把复仇者送进牢里去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.51,0:12:30.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You put the Strangler behind bars
Dialogue: 1,0:12:30.77,0:12:34.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,至少那个黄色白痴不会威胁到我了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.77,0:12:34.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,At least I'm safe from that yellow idiot
Dialogue: 1,0:12:34.48,0:12:35.23,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老弟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.48,0:12:35.23,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, Mack
Dialogue: 1,0:12:36.15,0:12:37.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你犯什么事进来的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.15,0:12:37.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are you in for?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:41.28,起司 特殊标题,,0,0,0,,{\fad(273,270)}恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:42.99,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(344,498)\frz28}分镜总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.53,0:12:46.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1096,976.667)}翻译{\fnArial}: 1440kHz
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.32,0:12:44.95,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28\pos(282,456)}分镜
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:46.87,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28\pos(398,310)}编剧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:48.78,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28\pos(342,406)}动画总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:48.78,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz28\pos(524,694)}创意总监
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.12,0:12:48.78,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1034.667,976.667)}本字幕仅限学习交流\N严禁用于商业用途
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.87,0:12:53.20,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(772,216)}恶作剧宫殿
Dialogue: 1,0:12:49.58,0:12:51.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  我们到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.58,0:12:51.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, Patrick, here it is
Dialogue: 1,0:12:51.70,0:12:53.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶作剧宫殿
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.70,0:12:53.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the Palace of Pranks
Dialogue: 1,0:12:53.47,0:12:56.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全裤头村最厉害的新奇道具商店
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.47,0:12:56.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the greatest novelty shop in Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:12:56.47,0:12:58.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最棒的恶作剧家都会来这买东西
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.47,0:12:58.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All the greatest pranksters shop here
Dialogue: 1,0:12:58.90,0:13:01.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我就在这买了恶作剧道具脆脆果仁罐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.90,0:13:01.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is where I got my gag seanut brittle can
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:01.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(688,280)}脆脆果仁
Dialogue: 1,0:13:01.59,0:13:03.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  脆脆果仁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.59,0:13:03.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, boy, seanut brittle
Dialogue: 1,0:13:03.40,0:13:04.10,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.40,0:13:04.10,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me
Dialogue: 1,0:13:04.10,0:13:05.80,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星等等  忘了里面有机关吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.10,0:13:05.80,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, wait, it's a booby trap, remember?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:05.98,0:13:07.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,少来了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.98,0:13:07.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice try, SquarePants
Dialogue: 1,0:13:07.76,0:13:09.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你这回肯定耍不到我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.76,0:13:09.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but it's not going to work this time
Dialogue: 1,0:13:09.78,0:13:12.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我要吃到你那好吃的脆脆果仁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.78,0:13:12.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm going to have some of your delicious seanut brittle
Dialogue: 1,0:13:13.35,0:13:14.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脆脆果仁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:14.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Where's the seanut brittle?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:16.73,0:13:19.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,每次你一说这话就更好笑了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.73,0:13:19.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That gets funnier every time you say it, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:13:19.36,0:13:20.82,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,走了  我们快进去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:20.82,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, let's go inside
Dialogue: 1,0:13:21.11,0:13:22.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脆脆果仁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.11,0:13:22.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Seanut brittle
Dialogue: 1,0:13:26.74,0:13:30.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,便宜的塑料道具味最好闻了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.74,0:13:28.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nothing compares to the smell
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.37,0:13:30.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,of cheap plastic novelty items
Dialogue: 1,0:13:30.25,0:13:31.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶作剧  小道具
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.25,0:13:31.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pranks, gags
Dialogue: 1,0:13:31.08,0:13:33.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有恶心玩具一眼望不到边
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.08,0:13:33.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and gross-out toys as far as the eye can see
Dialogue: 1,0:13:33.91,0:13:36.58,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我说的是不是都很对啊  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.91,0:13:36.58,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Isn't it everything I said it would be, Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:36.96,0:13:37.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脆脆果仁
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:37.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Seanut brittle
Dialogue: 1,0:13:39.13,0:13:40.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是  又来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.13,0:13:40.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Darn it, not again
Dialogue: 1,0:13:42.50,0:13:44.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很高兴又见到你了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.50,0:13:44.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good to see you, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:13:44.14,0:13:46.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我的头号顾客最近过得怎样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.14,0:13:46.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How's my number one customer doing?
Dialogue: 1,0:13:46.68,0:13:47.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还不错  法兰克
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:47.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Great, Frank
Dialogue: 1,0:13:47.56,0:13:48.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是我朋友派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.56,0:13:48.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,This is my friend, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:13:48.76,0:13:50.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他也想当恶作剧家
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:50.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,He wants to become a prankster, too
Dialogue: 1,0:13:50.43,0:13:52.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,很高兴认识你  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.43,0:13:52.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, pleasure to meet you, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:13:55.77,0:13:57.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这是你的第一课  孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.77,0:13:57.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's your first lesson, son
Dialogue: 1,0:13:57.69,0:13:59.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一切恶作剧的祖师爷
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.69,0:13:59.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The granddaddy of all pranks
Dialogue: 1,0:13:59.81,0:14:01.13,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,握手整蛊电击器
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.81,0:14:01.13,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the joy buzzer
Dialogue: 1,0:14:01.13,0:14:02.11,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.13,0:14:02.11,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't get it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:02.11,0:14:03.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用懂的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:03.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You don't have to get it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:03.57,0:14:06.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,恶作剧就是给恶作剧家整着玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.57,0:14:06.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The prank is for the enjoyment of the prankster
Dialogue: 1,0:14:06.82,0:14:09.87,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  这位法兰克可是个大师
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.82,0:14:09.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You see, Patrick, Frank here is the master
Dialogue: 1,0:14:09.87,0:14:12.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我所有恶作剧知识都是跟他学的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.87,0:14:12.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I learned all I know about pranks from him
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.35,0:14:13.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,法兰克  看看你都有些什么货
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.35,0:14:13.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Frank, let's see what you've got
Dialogue: 1,0:14:14.09,0:14:15.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这份是今天早上刚进的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.09,0:14:15.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, this came in just this morning
Dialogue: 1,0:14:16.05,0:14:16.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,吃点口香糖
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.05,0:14:16.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Have some gum
Dialogue: 1,0:14:20.71,0:14:23.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,爆炸口香糖  只要九块九毛五
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.71,0:14:23.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Exploding chewing gum, only $9.95
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.88,0:14:23.46,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(602,716)}爆炸糖
Dialogue: 1,0:14:23.68,0:14:24.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.68,0:14:24.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I don't get it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:25.09,0:14:26.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一块钱能买什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.09,0:14:26.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What can we get for one dollar?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:26.89,0:14:29.66,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一块钱可以买到这张假道具钱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.89,0:14:29.66,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,One dollar will get you this fake gag dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:14:29.66,0:14:32.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让你朋友以为你真的有一块钱
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:30.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fool your friends into thinking
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.93,0:14:32.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you've got a real dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:14:32.36,0:14:33.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.36,0:14:33.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What else have you got?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:33.47,0:14:34.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放屁坐垫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.47,0:14:34.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A whoopee cushion?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:34.65,0:14:35.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.65,0:14:35.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nah
Dialogue: 1,0:14:35.50,0:14:36.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,假呕吐物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.50,0:14:36.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Fake vomit
Dialogue: 1,0:14:36.68,0:14:37.35,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:37.35,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:14:37.53,0:14:38.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真呕吐物
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.53,0:14:38.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Real vomit
Dialogue: 1,0:14:39.60,0:14:40.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就没什么好货吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.60,0:14:40.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't you have anything good?
Dialogue: 1,0:14:41.02,0:14:44.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我倒是特地留了一样恶作剧道具
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.02,0:14:44.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, there is one prank that I've been saving
Dialogue: 1,0:14:44.15,0:14:46.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给顶级头号恶作剧家用
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:46.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,for a real top-of-the-line prankster
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:49.15,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(726,720)}隐身喷雾\N危险
Dialogue: 1,0:14:46.94,0:14:48.95,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,隐身喷雾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:48.95,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Invisible spray
Dialogue: 1,0:14:50.49,0:14:52.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,隐身喷雾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.49,0:14:52.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Invisible spray
Dialogue: 1,0:14:52.57,0:14:53.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可我看得到这玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.57,0:14:53.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But I can see it
Dialogue: 1,0:14:54.05,0:14:57.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  想想用这玩意能做啥恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.05,0:14:55.87,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee, Patrick, just think of the pranks
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.87,0:14:57.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we could pull with this
Dialogue: 1,0:14:58.04,0:14:59.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,选得好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.04,0:14:59.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good choice
Dialogue: 1,0:14:59.47,0:15:01.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,小心点使那玩意  孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.47,0:15:01.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Now, be careful with that stuff, boys
Dialogue: 1,0:15:01.25,0:15:02.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,会弄脏衣服的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:02.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It stains clothes
Dialogue: 1,0:15:02.89,0:15:03.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了  法兰克
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.89,0:15:03.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks, Frank
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.17,0:15:07.59,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(650,792)}隐身喷雾
Dialogue: 1,0:15:04.71,0:15:06.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,到手了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.71,0:15:06.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here it is, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:15:06.09,0:15:07.59,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,终极恶作剧道具
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.09,0:15:07.59,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,the ultimate prank
Dialogue: 1,0:15:07.59,0:15:09.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,隐身喷雾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.59,0:15:09.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Invisible spray
Dialogue: 1,0:15:09.15,0:15:10.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要用这玩意来干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.15,0:15:10.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What are we going to do with it?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:10.77,0:15:11.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.77,0:15:11.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know
Dialogue: 1,0:15:11.64,0:15:14.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,去喷公园长椅  再坐上去
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:14.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll go spray the park bench and then sit on it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:14.91,0:15:18.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,路人会当我们在浮空
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.91,0:15:18.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and when people walk by, we'll be floating in midair
Dialogue: 1,0:15:19.64,0:15:21.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,他们居然浮空了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.64,0:15:21.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,They're floating in midair
Dialogue: 1,0:15:21.06,0:15:22.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么做到的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:22.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How do they do that?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:23.23,0:15:25.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好终极的恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.23,0:15:25.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's the ultimate prank
Dialogue: 1,0:15:25.25,0:15:26.78,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好点子  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.25,0:15:26.78,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good idea, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:15:26.95,0:15:28.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那就开始吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.95,0:15:28.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, let's get started
Dialogue: 1,0:15:29.15,0:15:30.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我准备好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.15,0:15:30.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm ready
Dialogue: 1,0:15:31.66,0:15:33.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你为什么要把裤子脱掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.66,0:15:33.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Any particular reason you took your pants off?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:33.79,0:15:35.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这玩意会弄脏衣服  对不
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.79,0:15:35.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, that stuff stains clothes, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:15:36.24,0:15:38.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,说得确实  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.24,0:15:38.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That it does, Patrick, that it does
Dialogue: 1,0:15:38.79,0:15:39.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,想得真周到
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.79,0:15:39.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Good thinking
Dialogue: 1,0:15:39.63,0:15:40.62,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给  你来拿一会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.63,0:15:40.62,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, hold this a second
Dialogue: 1,0:15:42.00,0:15:43.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  罐子给我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:43.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, Patrick, give me the can
Dialogue: 1,0:15:43.89,0:15:46.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,既然喷公园长椅是我想出来的点子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.89,0:15:46.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think since spraying the park bench was my idea
Dialogue: 1,0:15:46.92,0:15:48.44,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就应该让我来喷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.92,0:15:48.44,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I should get to spray it
Dialogue: 1,0:15:48.44,0:15:50.92,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星  喷公园长椅是我的点子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.44,0:15:50.92,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick, spraying the park bench was my idea
Dialogue: 1,0:15:50.92,0:15:53.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  可我之前说那是好点子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.92,0:15:53.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, but I said it was a good idea
Dialogue: 1,0:15:53.49,0:15:54.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快点给我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.49,0:15:54.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Give me that thing
Dialogue: 1,0:16:00.56,0:16:02.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,隐身喷雾还真有用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:02.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The invisible spray works
Dialogue: 1,0:16:02.14,0:16:03.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,大家看向右边
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.14,0:16:03.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And on your right if you look
Dialogue: 1,0:16:03.77,0:16:07.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可以看到两个裸男在抢一罐颜料
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.77,0:16:07.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,you'll see two naked guys fighting over a can of paint
Dialogue: 1,0:16:09.78,0:16:10.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,老天爷啊  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.78,0:16:10.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, my gosh, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:16:10.99,0:16:12.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快帮我找衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.99,0:16:12.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,help me find our clothes
Dialogue: 1,0:16:16.12,0:16:18.85,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我得用手拿给你了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.12,0:16:18.85,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to hand it to you, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:16:18.85,0:16:20.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你样子真好笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.85,0:16:20.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You look kind of funny
Dialogue: 1,0:16:21.37,0:16:23.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,右手  你哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:23.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Righty, where are you?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:23.83,0:16:25.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不许欺负右手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.83,0:16:25.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No one messes with Righty
Dialogue: 1,0:16:26.54,0:16:27.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看看你有什么感想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.54,0:16:27.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll see how you like it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:29.67,0:16:32.09,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是不是给你了空洞的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.67,0:16:32.09,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Kind of gives you an empty feeling, huh?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:32.88,0:16:33.72,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.88,0:16:33.72,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:16:35.01,0:16:36.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看得出来你什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.01,0:16:36.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I see what you mean
Dialogue: 1,0:16:39.31,0:16:41.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没有肚量就没有成功
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.31,0:16:41.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No guts, no glory
Dialogue: 1,0:16:42.73,0:16:45.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,75,,几句冷笑话后
Dialogue: 1,0:16:46.69,0:16:48.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这玩意应该是空了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.69,0:16:48.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think this thing is empty
Dialogue: 1,0:16:48.25,0:16:49.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不可能吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.25,0:16:49.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, it can't be
Dialogue: 1,0:16:49.67,0:16:52.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这下还怎么搞终极恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.67,0:16:52.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,How are we going to pull off the ultimate prank?
Dialogue: 1,0:16:52.00,0:16:53.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,可谢谢你了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:53.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thanks a lot, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:16:53.28,0:16:54.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,隐身喷雾都被你用光了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.28,0:16:54.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You used the last of it
Dialogue: 1,0:16:56.82,0:16:58.20,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我好像找到裤子了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:16:58.20,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I think I found our pants
Dialogue: 1,0:16:59.83,0:17:01.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,给  这条是你的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.83,0:17:01.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Here, these are yours
Dialogue: 1,0:17:01.46,0:17:02.70,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别管裤子了  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.46,0:17:02.70,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Forget the pants, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:17:02.70,0:17:04.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,回家把身上的喷雾都洗掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.70,0:17:04.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's get home and wash this paint off
Dialogue: 1,0:17:04.65,0:17:06.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  能问下现在几点了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.65,0:17:06.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Hey, SpongeBob, do you know what time it is?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:07.08,0:17:07.63,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好啊  现在
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.08,0:17:07.63,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, it's
Dialogue: 1,0:17:08.21,0:17:10.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,看不见点半
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.21,0:17:10.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,half past invisible
Dialogue: 1,0:17:10.16,0:17:11.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,时候也不早了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.16,0:17:11.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Gee, it's getting late
Dialogue: 1,0:17:11.93,0:17:13.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来问下这个人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.93,0:17:13.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's ask this guy
Dialogue: 1,0:17:13.06,0:17:14.73,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,先生  能问下现在几点吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.06,0:17:14.73,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, sir, but do you have the time?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:14.73,0:17:16.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好的  现在两点五十
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.73,0:17:16.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Sure, it's ten to 3:00
Dialogue: 1,0:17:16.69,0:17:17.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.69,0:17:17.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Thank you
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.45,0:17:18.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:18.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it
Dialogue: 1,0:17:18.36,0:17:19.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用啥玩意
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.36,0:17:19.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't mention what?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.01,0:17:20.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,是谁说的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.01,0:17:20.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who said that?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:20.98,0:17:21.60,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.98,0:17:21.60,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me
Dialogue: 1,0:17:22.39,0:17:23.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.39,0:17:23.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ghosts
Dialogue: 1,0:17:27.35,0:17:28.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不是鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.35,0:17:28.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm no ghost
Dialogue: 1,0:17:28.61,0:17:31.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那人跟他那个会开船的眼球真胆小
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.61,0:17:31.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The nerve of that guy and his driving eyeballs
Dialogue: 1,0:17:31.53,0:17:33.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等一下  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.53,0:17:33.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait a second, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:17:33.15,0:17:35.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我脑子生出了个好办法
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:35.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,my brain just hatched an idea
Dialogue: 1,0:17:35.24,0:17:36.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,生来给我听
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.24,0:17:36.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Lay it on me
Dialogue: 1,0:17:36.36,0:17:38.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们隐身了  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:38.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Okay, we're invisible, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:17:38.41,0:17:39.32,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.41,0:17:39.32,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:17:39.74,0:17:41.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是那人以为我们是鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.74,0:17:41.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,If that guy thought we were ghosts
Dialogue: 1,0:17:41.74,0:17:44.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们就能缠上裤头村的所有人了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:44.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we could haunt everybody in Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 1,0:17:44.54,0:17:46.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,好一个终极恶作剧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.54,0:17:46.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's the ultimate prank
Dialogue: 1,0:17:46.92,0:17:48.14,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,击个掌
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:48.14,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,High five
Dialogue: 1,0:17:48.14,0:17:51.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一起去吓几个笨蛋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.14,0:17:51.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Let's go scare us some suckers
Dialogue: 1,0:18:00.10,0:18:02.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,奇怪  我明明听到有说话声的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.10,0:18:02.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's funny, I thought I heard voices
Dialogue: 1,0:18:03.85,0:18:06.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我明明把这杯花生汁放桌子上的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:06.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I thought I left that glass of peanut juice on the table
Dialogue: 1,0:18:06.56,0:18:09.31,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我昨天不是把这个旧台灯扔了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:09.31,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And didn't I toss that old lamp out yesterday?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:09.31,0:18:11.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我什么时候淘到了这么多
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.31,0:18:11.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And since when did I acquire all these
Dialogue: 1,0:18:11.65,0:18:13.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星的肖像画
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.65,0:18:13.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,portraits of Patrick?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:16.90,0:18:19.03,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.90,0:18:19.03,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're ghosts
Dialogue: 1,0:18:22.24,0:18:24.08,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,果然是你们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.24,0:18:24.08,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I knew it was you guys
Dialogue: 1,0:18:24.08,0:18:26.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.08,0:18:26.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,All right, joke's over
Dialogue: 1,0:18:26.16,0:18:27.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,床单都拿掉
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.16,0:18:27.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Take off the sheets
Dialogue: 1,0:18:28.79,0:18:29.88,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还真的是鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.79,0:18:29.88,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It is ghosts
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.22,0:18:40.05,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(910,350)}德克萨斯
Dialogue: 1,0:18:42.14,0:18:44.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,天啊  她被吓得不轻
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.14,0:18:44.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Boy, we really scared her
Dialogue: 1,0:18:45.52,0:18:48.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,谁会是我们的下一个受害者呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.52,0:18:48.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Who's going to be our next victim?
Dialogue: 1,0:18:48.48,0:18:51.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,更好的问法是  谁不是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.48,0:18:51.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,A better question would be, "Who isn't?"
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.15,0:18:55.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,双层深海低脂黑蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.15,0:18:55.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Double-dark deep-sea light diet cake
Dialogue: 1,0:18:56.69,0:18:58.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你马上就是我的了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.69,0:18:58.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You will soon be mine
Dialogue: 1,0:19:06.04,0:19:13.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.04,0:19:13.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ghosts
Dialogue: 1,0:19:20.93,0:19:22.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.93,0:19:22.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ghosts
Dialogue: 1,0:19:24.35,0:19:26.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,卡哇帮嘎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.35,0:19:26.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Cowabunga
Dialogue: 1,0:19:27.22,0:19:28.06,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.22,0:19:28.06,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ghosts
Dialogue: 1,0:19:29.35,0:19:34.15,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.35,0:19:34.15,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ghosts
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:35.27,注释,,0,0,0,,[ toast（面包）与 ghost（鬼）谐音 ]
Dialogue: 1,0:19:34.15,0:19:35.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,面包啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.15,0:19:35.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Toast
Dialogue: 1,0:19:35.27,0:19:36.86,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.27,0:19:36.86,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ghosts
