Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.65,0:19:43.45,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(616,754)}全城被吓
Dialogue: 1,0:19:37.44,0:19:38.69,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,官方认证了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:38.69,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's official
Dialogue: 1,0:19:38.69,0:19:40.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们是史上最棒的恶作剧家
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.69,0:19:40.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we're the greatest pranksters ever
Dialogue: 1,0:19:40.65,0:19:43.49,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,全镇人都以为我们是鬼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.65,0:19:43.49,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The whole town thinks we're ghosts
Dialogue: 1,0:19:43.91,0:19:44.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.91,0:19:44.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:19:45.08,0:19:47.29,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,最后再吓一位
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:47.29,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,There's only one guy left to scare
Dialogue: 1,0:19:47.29,0:19:50.21,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,裤头村所有人就都全被咱整过了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:50.21,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and we'll have pranked everybody in Bikini Bottom
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:52.42,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(950,156)}唯有蟹老板暂未被鬼上身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:52.42,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1000,680)}他表示{\fnArial}"{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}我不怕鬼{\fnArial}"
Dialogue: 1,0:19:50.21,0:19:52.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\bord10}蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.21,0:19:52.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\bord10}Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:54.96,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz180\pos(424,914)}唯有蟹老板暂未被鬼上身
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.42,0:19:54.96,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\frz180\pos(430,396)}他表示{\fnArial}"{\fnAdobe 黑体 Std R}我不怕鬼{\fnArial}"
Dialogue: 1,0:19:52.64,0:19:54.96,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,{\bord10}上面写着他不怕鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.64,0:19:54.96,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,{\bord10}It says he isn't scared of ghosts
Dialogue: 1,0:19:55.29,0:19:57.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等着瞧好了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.29,0:19:57.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We'll see about that
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.88,0:19:59.80,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(560,380)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.80,0:20:01.26,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(314,594)}关
Dialogue: 1,0:20:00.26,0:20:01.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:01.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Ghosts
Dialogue: 1,0:20:02.68,0:20:04.34,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我才不怕什么鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.68,0:20:04.34,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I ain't afraid of no ghosts
Dialogue: 1,0:20:04.85,0:20:08.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,水手都知道驱鬼的办法
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.85,0:20:08.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Every sailor knows a ghost won't come near a fella
Dialogue: 1,0:20:08.22,0:20:11.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,就是戴着斑点领巾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.22,0:20:11.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,as long as he's wearing his spotted neckerchief
Dialogue: 1,0:20:11.28,0:20:13.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还带着风干的海妖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.28,0:20:13.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and his dried-up sea leprechaun
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:15.61,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(728,336)}狐媚
Dialogue: 1,0:20:13.56,0:20:15.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,带点金子也算不了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.56,0:20:15.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And a bit of gold never hurt
Dialogue: 1,0:20:15.83,0:20:17.48,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不过为了以防万一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.83,0:20:17.48,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,But to be on the safe side
Dialogue: 1,0:20:17.48,0:20:20.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我穿的裤子上还打了个结
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:20.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm also wearing me pants in a melvin knot
Dialogue: 1,0:20:20.40,0:20:22.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,脚上还戴了木制防抖支撑器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.40,0:20:22.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,got me shivering timber brace
Dialogue: 1,0:20:22.61,0:20:26.83,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我脖子后边的毛也用胶带揭下来了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.61,0:20:26.83,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,and the hairs on the back of me neck are taped down
Dialogue: 1,0:20:27.16,0:20:30.76,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我还披了件防鬼用的盔甲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.16,0:20:30.76,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And I'm all wrapped up in a suit of anti-ghost armor
Dialogue: 1,0:20:30.76,0:20:32.50,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,要是全都失效了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.76,0:20:32.50,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,And if none of this stuff works
Dialogue: 1,0:20:32.50,0:20:34.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,还有秘密武器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.50,0:20:34.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got me secret weapon
Dialogue: 1,0:20:34.47,0:20:36.67,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鬼怪转移器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.47,0:20:36.67,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The specter deflector
Dialogue: 1,0:20:37.13,0:20:40.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们这些鬼快来抓我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.13,0:20:40.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So just try and get me, you ghosts
Dialogue: 1,0:20:40.30,0:20:41.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,放马过来
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:41.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Bring it on
Dialogue: 1,0:20:44.22,0:20:46.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.22,0:20:46.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.22,0:20:46.55,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.22,0:20:46.55,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 1,0:20:46.93,0:20:50.39,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  我们要来缠上你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.93,0:20:50.39,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Krabs, we've come to haunt you
Dialogue: 1,0:20:50.60,0:20:52.43,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,退后  我全副武装
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.60,0:20:52.43,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Stay back, I'm well-armed
Dialogue: 1,0:20:56.10,0:20:57.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我警告你们
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.10,0:20:57.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I'm warning you
Dialogue: 1,0:21:08.03,0:21:10.74,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,一定要逃出去
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.03,0:21:10.74,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I got to get out of here
Dialogue: 1,0:21:11.37,0:21:13.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你逃不出去的  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.37,0:21:13.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You can't escape, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:21:13.91,0:21:17.00,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们把门粘起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.91,0:21:17.00,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We glued the door shut
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.46,0:21:17.00,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1080,828)}胶水
Dialogue: 1,0:21:17.00,0:21:18.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们抓不到我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.00,0:21:18.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You'll never get me
Dialogue: 1,0:21:21.59,0:21:23.77,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,逃不掉的  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.59,0:21:23.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Nice try, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:21:23.77,0:21:27.26,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们把玻璃都换成橡胶了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.77,0:21:27.26,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,but we replaced all the glass with rubber
Dialogue: 1,0:21:29.68,0:21:31.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,太晚了  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.68,0:21:31.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Too late, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:21:31.22,0:21:34.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们已经把马桶堵上了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:34.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,we've already clogged all the toilets
Dialogue: 1,0:21:35.12,0:21:37.90,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鬼魂  我求你们放我一马吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.12,0:21:37.90,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please, spirits, leave me be
Dialogue: 1,0:21:39.23,0:21:41.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,整到他了  海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.23,0:21:41.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We got him good, SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.16,0:21:41.98,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,等等  派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.16,0:21:41.98,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Wait, Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:21:41.98,0:21:44.41,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我又想到了个点子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.98,0:21:44.41,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I've got one more idea
Dialogue: 1,0:21:44.41,0:21:47.36,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你要付出代价  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.41,0:21:47.36,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You're going to pay, Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:21:47.82,0:21:49.57,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,鬼魂不要  拜托
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.82,0:21:49.57,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, spirits, please
Dialogue: 1,0:21:49.57,0:21:50.99,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,代价
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.57,0:21:50.99,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pay
Dialogue: 1,0:21:50.99,0:21:51.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.99,0:21:51.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:21:51.54,0:21:53.45,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,代价
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.54,0:21:53.45,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Pay
Dialogue: 1,0:21:53.67,0:21:54.91,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.67,0:21:54.91,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No
Dialogue: 1,0:21:54.91,0:21:56.75,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不要烧我的钱
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.91,0:21:56.75,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't burn me dollar
Dialogue: 1,0:22:02.46,0:22:06.47,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,哟哟哟  这不是海绵宝宝跟派大星吗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:06.47,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, well, well, if it isn't SpongeBob and Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:22:08.01,0:22:10.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我不认识你说的是谁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.01,0:22:10.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I know not these names of which you speak
Dialogue: 1,0:22:11.43,0:22:12.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.43,0:22:12.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob
Dialogue: 1,0:22:12.93,0:22:15.27,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,海绵宝宝  我们显形回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.93,0:22:15.27,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,SpongeBob, we're visible again
Dialogue: 1,0:22:18.35,0:22:22.61,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,原来你们两个就是裤头村的鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.35,0:22:22.61,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,So you two are the Bikini Bottom ghosts
Dialogue: 1,0:22:22.61,0:22:24.40,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真的很对不起  蟹老板
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.61,0:22:24.40,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We're really sorry, Mr. Krabs
Dialogue: 1,0:22:24.40,0:22:26.53,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,求你别把我们剁成块吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.40,0:22:26.53,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Please don't chop us up into little pieces and eat them
Dialogue: 1,0:22:27.49,0:22:29.28,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没事  我是吃素的嬉皮士
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.49,0:22:29.28,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,come on, boys, I'm hip
Dialogue: 1,0:22:29.70,0:22:32.17,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我在你们这把年纪也搞恶作剧的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.70,0:22:32.17,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,I pulled my share of pranks when I was your age
Dialogue: 1,0:22:32.17,0:22:33.24,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,让我笑得可开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.17,0:22:33.24,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,had me some laughs
Dialogue: 1,0:22:33.62,0:22:35.22,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们今晚就是这样的  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.62,0:22:35.22,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That's what we did tonight, right?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:35.22,0:22:36.89,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我们笑得可开心了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.22,0:22:36.89,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We had a good laugh
Dialogue: 1,0:22:36.89,0:22:38.16,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,来吧  一起笑
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.89,0:22:38.16,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Come on, laugh with me
Dialogue: 1,0:22:48.47,0:22:51.30,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们为什么要光着身子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.47,0:22:51.30,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Any particular reason you boys are naked?
Dialogue: 1,0:22:51.64,0:22:53.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,隐身喷雾会弄脏衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.64,0:22:53.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the invisible paint stains clothes
Dialogue: 1,0:22:54.89,0:22:55.93,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,那是当然了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.89,0:22:55.93,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Of course it does
Dialogue: 1,0:22:55.93,0:22:59.46,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,快回家吧  免得有谁看到你们裸体
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.93,0:22:57.77,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Well, you two better hurry home
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.77,0:22:59.46,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,before someone sees you nude
Dialogue: 1,0:22:59.46,0:23:02.65,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,对啊  真那样我会被尬死的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.46,0:23:02.65,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I think I'd die of embarrassment if that happened
Dialogue: 1,0:23:02.65,0:23:03.52,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,我也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.65,0:23:03.52,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Me, too
Dialogue: 1,0:23:04.02,0:23:05.54,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,这种事可不能有  对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.02,0:23:05.54,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,No, wouldn't want that, would we?
Dialogue: 1,0:23:05.54,0:23:06.51,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,都这么晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.54,0:23:06.51,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,It's getting late now
Dialogue: 1,0:23:06.51,0:23:08.07,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,你们两个恶作剧家该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.51,0:23:08.07,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,You pranksters better get going
Dialogue: 1,0:23:08.40,0:23:11.25,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板  谢谢你对我们这么好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.40,0:23:11.25,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Mr. Krabs, thanks for being such a good sport
Dialogue: 1,0:23:11.25,0:23:12.37,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,不用谢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.25,0:23:12.37,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Don't mention it
Dialogue: 1,0:23:12.59,0:23:15.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹老板啊  总是会为我着想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.59,0:23:15.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,That Mr. Krabs, always looking out for me
Dialogue: 1,0:23:15.04,0:23:16.04,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,真是个好人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.04,0:23:16.04,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,What a guy
Dialogue: 1,0:23:16.04,0:23:16.79,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.04,0:23:16.79,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah
Dialogue: 1,0:23:17.25,0:23:19.71,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,蟹堡王倾情奉献
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.25,0:23:19.71,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,The Krusty Krab presents
Dialogue: 1,0:23:19.71,0:23:22.94,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,活生生的裸体恶作剧家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.71,0:23:22.94,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,live nude pranksters
Dialogue: 1,0:23:22.94,0:23:26.42,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,由裤头村的鬼领衔主演
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.94,0:23:26.42,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Starring the Bikini Bottom ghosts
Dialogue: 1,0:23:37.47,0:23:38.81,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,派大星
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.47,0:23:38.81,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Patrick
Dialogue: 1,0:23:38.81,0:23:39.64,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.81,0:23:39.64,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.02,0:23:44.23,画面内容,,0,0,0,,{\pos(474,364)}蟹堡王
Dialogue: 1,0:23:40.02,0:23:43.56,标准-Chi,,0,0,0,,早知道就买放屁坐垫了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.02,0:23:43.56,标准-Eng,,0,0,0,,We should have bought the whoopee cushion
